description:
We can all pretty much agree no matter where you stand on all the things that have or are going on.. 2020 has been a hell of a clusterfuck

But there’s 109 days left in it as of right now

You can sit and wait around, saying that your looking forward to 2021 to get here already

Or you can stop using 2020 as the excuse why you’re not where you want to be. Being mad about things going on didn’t stop you from reading a book, learning how to eat right, building and improving important relationships, learning a new skill or even simply going for a walk

If anything, 2020 has given most of us more time to do these very things and just like the guy who always says “diet starts Monday” many of you are in the same, if not worse place right now than you’d been if you just done a little bit

So, I know how I’m going to use these last 109 days...

The same way I’ve used everyone before it

On improving myself

You in?

#2020
#alwaysimproving
